               "text": "<p class=\"desc\"><img id=\"imgPlanckHistory\" onclick=\"htImageZoom('imgPlanckHistory', '0%')\" src=\"\" class=\"imgcenter\"/><b>Figura 1</b>: História do universo de acordo com o modelo Lambda-CDM (<htcite0>).</p>",
               "source": [
